nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE MAKING ITS WAY WESTWARD WELL TO THE EAST OF HAWAII...
summary: ...HENRIETTE MAKING ITS WAY WESTWARD WELL TO THE EAST OF HAWAII... As of 5:00 AM HST Thu Aug 07 the center of Henriette was located near 18.6, -135.5 with movement W at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
